프롬프트 6/12: Firebase 연동 및 소셜 로그인
[Goal] Integrate Firebase Authentication for user management.

[Instructions for AI Developer]

Firebase Integration: Initialize Firebase in your application.

Authentication UI: Add "Login" buttons to the header.

Login Methods: Implement "Sign in with Google" and "Sign in with Facebook".

Dynamic Header: When a user is logged in, replace the "Login" buttons with the user's profile picture. Clicking it should open a dropdown menu with the user's name and a "Logout" button.
해당 내용 반영해서 회원가입 및 소셜 로그인  기능을 추가시켜줘  